gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 121, Magic 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Magic, 121-111. Donovan Mitchell led the Cavaliers with 35 points, seven rebounds, six assists, and five 3PT as Darius Garland added 26 points and nine assists. Paolo Banchero dropped a career-high 42 points, along with six rebounds for Orlando in the loss. The Cavaliers improve to 12-9 as the Magic move to 14-7.
